HEADWORD: Campana
<hw>Cam*pa"na</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>campana</ets> bell. Cf. <er>Campanle</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>A church bell.</def>⟦br⟧
